00:05:51.133 --> 00:05:53.970
 SPEAKER 1: Chelsea asks, if we
use plug-ins, we run into features

00:05:53.970 --> 00:05:55.867
within the plug-ins
not being accessible

00:05:55.868 --> 00:05:57.440
and not having the access we need

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:59.240
to fix accessibility
issues directly.

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:01.630
Do you have any favorite
lists or resources

00:06:01.630 --> 00:06:03.970
to check on specific
plugin recommendations

00:06:03.971 --> 00:06:05.300
or known plug-in issues?

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:08.410
 AMBER: Hi, I'm Amber
Hinds, and I'm happy

00:06:08.410 --> 00:06:11.890
to answer this question about whether
or not there is a recommended list

00:06:11.890 --> 00:06:12.920
of plugins.

00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:16.160
But before I get to that list
of plugins, I want to start

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:21.810
by talking about some of the caveats,
or why it's really complicated

00:06:21.810 --> 00:06:26.010
to create a list of plugins
that are accessible.

00:06:26.010 --> 00:06:29.260
First of all,
there are a lot of plug-ins

00:06:29.260 --> 00:06:32.380
that may have a very
accessible front-end output

00:06:32.380 --> 00:06:34.710
or perhaps they have
zero front-end output

00:06:34.710 --> 00:06:37.600
and they don't impact the
front-end of your website at all,

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:41.190
but they have very
inaccessible back-ends.

00:06:41.190 --> 00:06:44.060
So if you're starting to
think about what is a list

00:06:44.060 --> 00:06:46.960
of accessible plug-ins we can use, I
think the first thing you would need

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:48.960
to know is whether you're
looking for plug-ins

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:51.460
that create accessible
front-ends or plug-ins

00:06:51.460 --> 00:06:55.140
that also have an accessible
admin interface for people

00:06:55.140 --> 00:06:58.320
with disabilities who may be
editing your WordPress website.

00:06:58.320 --> 00:07:02.310
And then once you know
that, I think the next thing

00:07:02.310 --> 00:07:06.160
that you really have to keep in
mind and what further complicates

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:10.130
creating this list is that
there are many WordPress plugins

00:07:10.130 --> 00:07:14.630
that are accessible but only
with specific configurations

00:07:14.630 --> 00:07:17.130
or settings enabled in that plugin.

00:07:17.130 --> 00:07:18.253
And then of course we know

00:07:18.254 --> 00:07:20.240
in WordPress things are
constantly changing.

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:25.540
There's always plug-in updates
and things that are being modified

00:07:25.540 --> 00:07:26.420
in plugins.

00:07:26.420 --> 00:07:30.190
And so creating a list of
accessible plug-ins is something

00:07:30.190 --> 00:07:31.060
that could change.

00:07:31.060 --> 00:07:34.150
There could be a website that
was very accessible today,

00:07:34.150 --> 00:07:36.540
and I'll put it on the list
and then they release an update

00:07:36.540 --> 00:07:39.130
and it's not going to be
accessible tomorrow or vice versa.

00:07:39.130 --> 00:07:41.480
There could be one that I
go, I look at and I assess

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:43.550
and I say, oh,
this doesn't work very well,

00:07:43.550 --> 00:07:47.470
and then they release a giant
accessibility improvement update,

00:07:47.470 --> 00:07:49.490
and now it works perfectly.

00:07:49.490 --> 00:07:54.260
Keep in mind also that there
is a just a sheer number

00:07:54.260 --> 00:07:56.620
of WordPress plug-ins
that are available.

00:07:56.620 --> 00:08:00.090
So I always have a hard time
when people ask me this,

00:08:00.090 --> 00:08:03.450
which page builder do you
recommend, for example.

00:08:03.450 --> 00:08:06.670
Well, I haven't tried all the
page builders, so it's really hard

00:08:06.670 --> 00:08:09.600
for me to go out and say,
this one is the best,

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:12.720
because how can I say it's the best
if I haven't tried all of them?

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:15.410
And so just the reality of
WordPress and how many plug-ins

00:08:15.410 --> 00:08:19.290
there are there, there might be
plug-ins that are really fabulous

00:08:19.290 --> 00:08:22.340
that I have just never
tested for accessibility.

00:08:23.400 --> 00:08:26.160
Now that said,
I don't want to leave you

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:31.250
with a super roundabout
answer and nothing concrete.

